<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Forest Conservation & Management</title>
    
    <!-- Google Fonts: Poppins -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <!-- Font Awesome Icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">

    <!-- CSS Styles -->
    <style>
        /* CSS Variables for Earthy Theme */
        :root {
            --primary-green: #2d6a4f;
            --light-green: #40916c;
            --dark-green: #1b4332;
            --accent-green: #d8f3dc;
            --text-dark: #1f2937;
            --text-light: #f3f4f6;
            --bg-color: #f8fafc;
            --warning-red: #e63946;
            --card-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            --glass-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
        }

        /* Basic Reset & Typography */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        h1, h2, h3, h4 {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--dark-green);
        }

        p {
            color: #4b5563;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }

        /* Reusable Classes */
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .section-padding {
            padding: 80px 0;
        }

        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--dark-green);
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--light-green);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* Scroll Reveal Animation Classes */
        .reveal {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateY(40px);
            transition: all 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .reveal.active {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */
        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        nav.scrolled {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            padding: 15px 0;
        }

        .nav-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--primary-green);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .nav-links li a {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: var(--dark-green);
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav-links li a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--primary-green);
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links li a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .menu-toggle {
            display: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            color: var(--dark-green);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(27, 67, 50, 0.7)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1448375240586-882707db888b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover fixed;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero-content h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
            animation: fadeInDown 1s ease;
        }

        .hero-content p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease 0.3s;
            animation-fill-mode: both;
        }

        /* Step-by-Step Section Styles */
        .steps-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .step-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .step-card:hover {
            transform: translateX(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .step-number {
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .step-content h3 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: var(--dark-green);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 50px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .about-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        }

        /* Grid Cards Generic Styles */
        .cards-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--primary-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--accent-green);
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            line-height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        /* Threats Section specific styling */
        #threats {
            background: #fff5f5;
        }
        
        #threats .section-title {
            color: var(--warning-red);
        }

        .threat-card {
            border-top: 5px solid var(--warning-red);
        }

        .threat-card .card-icon {
            color: var(--warning-red);
            background: rgba(230, 57, 70, 0.1);
        }

        /* Gallery Section Updated - Masonry & Interactive Overlays */
        #gallery {
            background: var(--dark-green);
            color: white;
        }

        #gallery .section-title { color: white; }
        #gallery .section-subtitle { color: var(--accent-green); }

        .gallery-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            height: 400px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            cursor: pointer;
            background: #000;
        }

        .gallery-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), filter 0.5s ease;
            opacity: 0.85;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover img {
            transform: scale(1.08);
            filter: saturate(1.2) contrast(1.1);
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .gallery-content {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.95) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 50%, transparent 100%);
            transform: translateY(60px);
            transition: transform 0.5s ease, background 0.5s ease;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover .gallery-content {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .gallery-tag {
            background: var(--light-green);
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .gallery-content h4 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .gallery-content p {
            color: #d1d5db;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease 0.2s;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover .gallery-content p {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .gallery-footer {
            margin-top: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.4s ease 0.3s;
        }

        .gallery-item:hover .gallery-footer {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Contact & Comments Section */
        .contact-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .contact-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        }

        .contact-card h3 {
            color: var(--primary-green);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-green);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .contact-info p {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .contact-info i {
            color: var(--light-green);
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            width: 20px;
        }

        .comment-box {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
        }

        .comment-form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .comment-form input, .comment-form textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            outline: none;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        .comment-form input:focus, .comment-form textarea:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-green);
        }

        .btn-submit {
            background: var(--primary-green);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            background: var(--dark-green);
        }

        .comment-list {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .comment-item {
            background: var(--bg-color);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary-green);
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease;
        }

        .comment-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .comment-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: var(--dark-green);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px 20px;
        }

        .project-team {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        .project-team h4 {
            color: var(--accent-green);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .team-members {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 15px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #d1d5db;
        }

        .team-member {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .social-links {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .social-links a {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--accent-green);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-links a:hover {
            transform: scale(1.2);
        }

        /* Keyframe Animations */
        @keyframes fadeInDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
            .hero-content h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .menu-toggle { display: block; }
            
            .nav-links {
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%;
                left: -100%;
                width: 100%;
                background: white;
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 20px;
                text-align: center;
                box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
                transition: left 0.3s ease;
            }

            .nav-links.active { left: 0; }
            .nav-links li a { color: var(--dark-green); display: block; padding: 10px 0;}
            
            .hero-content h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
            .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav id="navbar">
        <div class="container nav-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i> EcoForest
            </div>
            <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#importance">Importance</a></li>
                <li><a href="#threats">Threats</a></li>
                <li><a href="#conservation">Conservation</a></li>
                <li><a href="#steps">Steps</a></li>
                <li><a href="#gallery">Gallery</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle">
                <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Home / Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Forest Conservation & Management</h1>
            <p>Protecting the lungs of our planet. Join the movement to preserve biodiversity, combat climate change, and ensure a sustainable future for generations to come.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section-padding" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Understanding Forests</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle reveal">What is Forest Conservation and Management?</p>
            
            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-text reveal">
                    <h3>Preserving Nature's Balance</h3>
                    <p><strong>Forest Conservation</strong> is the practice of planting and maintaining forested areas for the benefit and sustainability of future generations. It involves protecting ecosystems from deforestation, pollution, and destructive human activities.</p>
                    <p><strong>Forest Management</strong> refers to the administrative, economic, legal, and social aspects of forest preservation. It includes scientific planning to ensure that timber harvesting, wildlife protection, and recreational uses are balanced sustainably.</p>
                    <p>Together, they form the foundation of environmental stability, ensuring our planet remains habitable and vibrant.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="reveal">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511497584788-876760111969?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Lush Green Forest" class="about-img">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Importance Section -->
    <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--accent-green);" id="importance">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Why Forests Matter</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle reveal">The crucial roles forests play in sustaining life on Earth</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-frog card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Biodiversity 🌿</h3>
                    <p>Forests are home to over 80% of terrestrial species of animals, plants, and insects. They provide critical habitats for countless endangered species.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-wind card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Oxygen Production 🌍</h3>
                    <p>Often called the 'lungs of the Earth', forests produce massive amounts of the oxygen we breathe while purifying the air we consume.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-cloud-sun-rain card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Climate Regulation 🌦️</h3>
                    <p>Trees absorb carbon dioxide, a major greenhouse gas, mitigating climate change and regulating regional rainfall and temperature.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-coins card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Economic Importance 💰</h3>
                    <p>Forests provide livelihoods for over 1.6 billion people worldwide, offering timber, medicine, food, and eco-tourism opportunities.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Threats Section -->
    <section class="section-padding" id="threats">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Major Threats</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle reveal">The dangers our global forests face today</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card threat-card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-tree-city card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Deforestation</h3>
                    <p>Mass clearing of land for agriculture, urbanization, and mining destroys vital ecosystems at an alarming rate daily.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card threat-card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-temperature-arrow-up card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Climate Change</h3>
                    <p>Changing weather patterns weaken forest health, causing droughts that make trees susceptible to pests and diseases.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card threat-card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-fire-flame-curved card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Forest Fires</h3>
                    <p>Both natural and human-caused wildfires decimate millions of acres annually, releasing stored carbon back into the atmosphere.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card threat-card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-axe card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Illegal Logging</h3>
                    <p>Unlawful harvesting of timber depletes valuable tree species and funds organized crime, ignoring sustainable practices.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Conservation Section -->
    <section class="section-padding" id="conservation">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Conservation Methods</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle reveal">How we can protect and restore our woodlands</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid">
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-seedling card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Afforestation</h3>
                    <p>Planting trees in barren lands to create new forests and reforesting degraded areas to restore lost ecosystems.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-gavel card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Government Laws</h3>
                    <p>Implementing and strictly enforcing national and international policies that ban illegal logging and protect national parks.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-recycle card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Sustainable Practices</h3>
                    <p>Using selective logging techniques and promoting eco-friendly consumer choices (like FSC-certified wood products).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="card reveal">
                    <i class="fas fa-users card-icon"></i>
                    <h3>Community Participation</h3>
                    <p>Empowering indigenous and local communities to manage forests, as they have generations of sustainable knowledge.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Steps for Conservation Section -->
    <section class="section-padding" style="background: var(--accent-green);" id="steps">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Actionable Steps</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle reveal">How you can actively conserve and manage forests</p>
            
            <div class="steps-container">
                <div class="step-card reveal">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Reduce, Reuse, Recycle Paper and Wood</h3>
                        <p>Minimize your dependence on paper and single-use wood products. Go digital whenever possible and always recycle paper to reduce the demand for fresh timber.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card reveal">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Support Certified Sustainable Products</h3>
                        <p>When buying wood or paper, look for certifications like FSC (Forest Stewardship Council). This ensures the products come from responsibly managed forests.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card reveal">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Participate in Reforestation Drives</h3>
                        <p>Join local NGOs and environmental groups in tree-planting initiatives. Planting native species helps restore local ecosystems.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card reveal">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Report Illegal Activities</h3>
                        <p>If you notice unauthorized clearing or signs of forest fire, alert the forest department immediately. Your quick action can save thousands of trees.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card reveal">
                    <div class="step-number">5</div>
                    <div class="step-content">
                        <h3>Spread Awareness</h3>
                        <p>Educate your community about the importance of forests. Awareness leads to collective action, the most powerful tool for conservation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Gallery Section -->
    <section class="section-padding" id="gallery">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title reveal">Ecosystem Explorer</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle reveal">Discover the intricate balance of different forest biomes</p>
            
            <div class="gallery-grid">
                <div class="gallery-item reveal">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1441974231531-c6227db76b6e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Sunlight in canopy">
                    <div class="gallery-content">
                        <span class="gallery-tag">Photosynthesis</span>
